going to my appointments which mostly in main city , beside going early in morning some of work even rush hour i find taking bus is so difficult and i have been in trouble several time of missing my appointments only because i can't locate the bus in time so I would suggest if you can add like bus times of each bus stop location in campaign app .  Thanks

This app is pretty helpful.

However, please do add allduring the wait times listed.

Also, sometimes the buses will arrive earlier than it says, but it should alway be on the earlier side.
